{"version": 2, "width": 90, "height": 30, "timestamp": 1774362452, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/bash", "TERM": "xterm-256color"}}
[0.007347, "o", "\u001b[H\u001b[2J\u001b[3J\r\n"]
[0.007763, "o", "\u001b[1;37m\r\n  ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ║   🛡️  MCP Shield                                          ║\r\n  ║   One-command security for MCP servers                    ║\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ║   Powered by agentgateway (Linux Foundation)              ║\r\n  ║   github.com/bcornish1797/mcp-shield                     ║\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.008859, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;33m  THE PROBLEM: Most MCP deployments have ZERO security\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[6.009753, "o", "  A typical Claude Desktop config:\r\n\r\n"]
[7.012809, "o", "  {\r\n    \"mcpServers\": {\r\n      \"filesystem\": {\r\n        \"command\": \"npx\",\r\n        \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem\", \"/tmp\"]\r\n      },\r\n      \"memory\": {\r\n        \"command\": \"npx\",\r\n        \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-memory\"]\r\n      },\r\n      \"github\": {\r\n        \"command\": \"npx\",\r\n        \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-github\"],\r\n        \"env\": {\r\n          \"GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN\": \"ghp_xxxxx\"\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n"]
[11.014383, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;31m  ⚠️  No authentication. No rate limiting. No audit logging.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[14.015577, "o", "\u001b[1;33m  THE SOLUTION: MCP Shield + agentgateway\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[16.01708, "o", "\u001b[1;32m  Step 1: Scan your existing MCP setup\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m$ node dist/index.js scan -f demo/sample-config.json\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[18.058718, "o", "\r\n🔍 Scanning for MCP server configurations...\r\n\r\n"]
[18.058951, "o", "  📁 Source:  claude-desktop\r\n  📄 File:    demo/sample-config.json\r\n"]
[18.058973, "o", "  🔧 Servers: 3 found\r\n\r\n"]
[18.059161, "o", "  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\r\n  │ MCP Servers                                            │\r\n  ├────────────────────┬──────────┬────────────────────────┤\r\n  │ Name               │ Type     │ Command/URL            │\r\n  ├────────────────────┼──────────┼────────────────────────┤\r\n  │ filesystem         │ stdio    │ npx                    │\r\n  │ memory             │ stdio    │ npx                    │\r\n  │ github             │ stdio    │ npx                    │\r\n"]
[18.059226, "o", "  └────────────────────┴──────────┴────────────────────────┘\r\n\r\n"]
[18.059248, "o", "  ⚠️  Security Assessment:\r\n    • Authentication:  NONE — any client can connect\r\n    • Rate Limiting:   NONE — no protection against abuse\r\n    • Audit Logging:   NONE — no visibility into tool usage\r\n    • Input Validation: NONE — tool arguments pass unchecked\r\n\r\n  💡 Run 'mcp-shield secure' to generate a secured configuration.\r\n\r\n"]
[21.066075, "o", "\u001b[1;32m  Step 2: Generate secured configuration\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m$ node dist/index.js secure -f demo/sample-config.json --rate-limit 60\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[23.107401, "o", "\r\n🛡️  MCP Shield — Generating secured configuration...\r\n\r\n"]
[23.107607, "o", "  📁 Found 3 MCP server(s) from claude-desktop\r\n\r\n"]
[23.109594, "o", "  🔐 Generating JWT keypair for authentication...\r\n"]
[23.114925, "o", "     Public key:  mcp-shield-output/keys/pub-key\r\n     Private key: mcp-shield-output/keys/priv-key.pem\r\n\r\n"]
[23.126975, "o", "  ✅ Secured configuration generated!\r\n\r\n  📂 Output files:\r\n     mcp-shield-output/gateway-config.yaml  — agentgateway configuration\r\n     mcp-shield-output/claude_desktop_config.json  — client config (points to gateway)\r\n"]
[23.127013, "o", "     mcp-shield-output/keys/  — JWT keypair\r\n"]
[23.127017, "o", "\r\n  🚀 To start the secured gateway:\r\n\r\n"]
[23.127238, "o", "     agentgateway -f mcp-shield-output/gateway-config.yaml\r\n\r\n  Then update your IDE to use the gateway endpoint:\r\n     http://localhost:3000/mcp\r\n\r\n  🛡️  Security features enabled:\r\n     • Authentication:  STRICT\r\n"]
[23.127281, "o", "     • Rate Limiting:   60 req/min\r\n     • CORS:            configured\r\n     • Audit Logging:   enabled\r\n     • Federation:      3 servers → 1 endpoint\r\n\r\n"]
[26.131555, "o", "\u001b[1;32m  Step 3: Start the secured gateway\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m$ mcp-shield start\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[30.133893, "o", "  \u001b[1;32m✅ Gateway started on port 3000\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[32.134803, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;32m  Step 4: Verify security\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m  Testing unauthenticated request...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[33.152595, "o", "  HTTP 401 — \u001b[1;31mBlocked! Authentication required.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[36.153649, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m  Checking OAuth discovery metadata...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[37.17259, "o", "  {\r\n      \"resource\": \"http://localhost:3000/mcp\",\r\n      \"authorization_servers\": [\r\n          \"mcp-shield\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"mcp_protocol_version\": \"2025-06-18\",\r\n      \"resource_type\": \"mcp-server\",\r\n      \"bearer_methods_supported\": [\r\n          \"header\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"scopes_supported\": [\r\n          \"read:all\",\r\n          \"write:all\",\r\n          \"admin\"\r\n      ]\r\n  }\r\n"]
[41.196878, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;37m\r\n  ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ║   ✅ MCP servers are now secured!                          ║\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ║   Features:                                               ║\r\n  ║   • JWT Authentication (strict mode)                      ║\r\n  ║   • Rate Limiting (token bucket, 60 req/min)              ║\r\n  ║   • CORS configured                                       ║\r\n  ║   • 3 servers federated → 1 secure endpoint               ║\r\n  ║   • OAuth 2.0 discovery metadata                          ║\r\n  ║   • Per-server endpoint isolation                          ║\r\n  ║   • Published to agentregistry                             ║\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ║   Built with:                                              ║\r\n  ║   • agentgateway (Linux Foundation)                        ║\r\n  ║   • agentregistry (Solo.io)                                ║\r\n  ║   • TypeScript + Commander.js                              ║\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ║   npm install -g mcp-shield                                ║\r\n  ║   github.com/bcornish1797/mcp-shield                      ║\r\n  ║                                                           ║\r\n  ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\u001b[0m\r\n"]
